    <sec>
      <title>Mathematical simplification, uncertainty, and sensitivity</title>
      <p>In this study, some equations have been modified from <xref rid="ref-9" ref-type="bibr">Caddy (1996)</xref> related to (i) the calculation of the duration of each subsequent gnomonic interval after the egg stage and (ii) the estimation of the constant proportion of the overall natural death rate (<italic>G</italic>) to improve the model performance during the computational process.</p>
      <p>The duration of the first gnomonic interval <inline-formula><alternatives><inline-graphic xlink:href="peerj-09-11229-i003.jpg"/><tex-math id="M5">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
