      <p>According to this equation, <italic>G</italic> can be estimated based on the total number of gnomonic intervals <inline-formula><alternatives><inline-graphic xlink:href="peerj-09-11229-i005.jpg"/><tex-math id="M8">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
